Julie Claire https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julie_Claire 0 Julie Claire is an American actress known for her recurring roles on the TV series Dirt and Devious Maids. She's also appeared in 24 as Eden Linley and in Web Therapy as Robin Griner. She appeared in the 2013 comedy film Movie 43.
